Infectious haematopoietic necrosis, Former Yug. Rep. of Macedonia
-----------------------------------------------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 10 Aug 2018 from Dr Zoran Atasanov, director, Food and Veterinary Agency, Ministry of Agriculture, Forestry and Water Economy Former Yug. Rep. of Macedonia, Skopje, Former Yug. Rep. of Macedonia

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 18 Jun 2018
Date of confirmation of the event: 18 Jun 2018
Reason for notification: recurrence of a listed disease
Date of previous occurrence: 2 May 2018
Manifestation of disease: sub-clinical infection
Causal agent: Infectious haematopoietic necrosis virus
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (advanced)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks
Summary of outbreaks:
Total outbreaks: 1
Outbreak 1: Gorno Dobrenoec, Gorno Dobrenoec, Drugovo, Kicevo
Date of start of the outbreak: 18 Jun 2018
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: farm
Water type: fresh water
Population type: farmed
Production system: semi-closed
Total animals affected:
Species / Morbidity / Mortality / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Killed and disposed of / Slaughtered
